
A CLI task runner                                                               
     
USAGE
    lets [command] [--flags]  
         
COMMANDS:
  bar           Print bar
  foo           Print foo
                  
INTERNAL COMMANDS:
  help          Help about any command
  self          Manage lets CLI itself
     
FLAGS
  --all         Show all commands (including the ones with _)
  -c --config   Config file (default is lets.yaml)
  -d --debug    Show debug logs (or use LETS_DEBUG=1). If used multiple times, shows more verbose logs
  -E --env      Set env variable for running command KEY=VALUE
  --exclude     Run all but excluded command(s) described in cmd as map
  -h --help     Help for lets
  --init        Create a new lets.yaml in the current folder
  --no-depends  Skip 'depends' for running command
  --only        Run only specified command(s) described in cmd as map
  -v --version  Version for lets

